Context:
This is a summary of where we are in the larger text so that we can better understand what will happen next.
This is the first Mishnah of the second perek of Maseches Kiddushin. The first perek began with a discussion of how _kiddushin_ can occur.
The first perek also went on various tangents related to how various acquisitions are made in general.
